      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-09-19T22:13:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "At the moment \"name\" should be \"buildbucket/\u003cbucket\u003e/\u003cbuilder name\u003e\" which is unique (I\u0027m going by the example in the doc). I think other configurations do it this way. Maybe it makes sense to drop \"Builder\" in that case? It\u0027s somewhat more general this way.",
      "parentUuid": "f67c8ce6_12046164",
      "revId": "9a7933ca5363d169e08873522de5a29bca832ec5",
