      "writtenOn": "2017-09-19T16:43:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "What\u0027s bad gonna happen if we do not search in buildbucket? I don\u0027t see a justification for this complexity\n\nI think if datastore does not have the state, we can just return UNKNOWN.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 105,
        "startChar": 17,
